title: Gold 3 (Plat MMR) Jungle Main LF Clash Team
body: Looking for a semi-competitive or even casual team in order to improve my play as an individual. Am open to criticism and willing to learn. Last season I placed; Plat 5 SoloQ, Gold 3 3v3 and Gold 5 Flex. Add me @Mørdekaiser on OCE or linguisticllama#1032 on discord.
